Package gov.tak.platform.ui

Class MotionEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.tak.platform.ui.MotionEvent
  • public final class MotionEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    User input event that covers touch and other pointer devices. This implementation is loosely based on Android's MotionEvent.
